text: Thorens may refer to: * Thorens, Swiss manufacturer of high-end audio equipment * Thorens-Glières, former commune in Haute-Savoie, France * Adèle Thorens Goumaz (born 1971), Swiss politician * Château de Thorens, castle in Thorens-Glières, Haute-Savoie, France * Pointe de Thorens, mountain of Savoie, France * Val Thorens, ski resort in Savoie, French Alps
title: Thorens (disambiguation)
